      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures; version control and audit trail maintained per FDA 21 CFR Part 820.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 used for all simulations. Vendor-supplied verification and validation documentation reviewed. Internal SOP-CAE-007 governs version control, access control, and change management. No open NCRs against the solver version. Gradation 2 achieved."
