      "rationale": "Three standard benchmark problems executed in Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 prior to production runs: cantilever beam deflection (0.3% error), circular plate bending (0.7% error), and cylindrical contact pressure (0.9% error). All within the 1% acceptance threshold. Gradation 2 achieved."
