      "rationale": "Three-level mesh convergence study conducted on the screw-rod interface region (coarse: 0.8 mm global, medium: 0.5 mm, fine: 0.3 mm). Stiffness QoI changed 4.1% (coarse-to-medium) and 1.2% (medium-to-fine). GCI for fine mesh = 1.8%. Production mesh uses medium density with local refinement at stress concentrations. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
