      "rationale": "Nonlinear static analysis with 200 load sub-steps. Force and displacement residual norms converged below 1e-5 for all increments across all 11 model instances. No bisection events or divergence warnings recorded in solver output logs. Gradation 1 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments completed by a second qualified analyst; discrepancies resolved prior to results extraction.",
      "rationale": "Model setup reviewed by a second senior FEA engineer (blinded to original analyst inputs) per SOP-CAE-012. Three minor discrepancies identified (load application point offset 0.2 mm, incorrect friction coefficient on one interface, missing fillet on rod geometry) and corrected prior to final runs. Corrected model re-reviewed and approved. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastic-plastic constitutive model with isotropic hardening appropriate for Ti-6Al-4V under quasi-static monotonic loading; contact formulation captures screw-rod interface behavior.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity (BISO) model used for Ti-6Al-4V components, consistent with quasi-static monotonic loading regime of ASTM F1717. Augmented Lagrange contact formulation applied at screw-rod and screw-block interfaces with friction coefficient 0.2. Model form supported by literature precedent (Nagaraja 2012, Goel 2006). Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
