      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from lot-specific coupon testing; geometry from calibrated CMM measurements of production hardware; torque preloads from assembly records.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (1.2 GPa) derived from Ti-6Al-4V ELI coupon testing (2023 dataset). Screw and rod geometry from CMM measurements (±0.01 mm). Assembly torque (6 Nm) from manufacturing records. Input parameter uncertainty quantified and propagated via ±1 SD sensitivity runs. Gradation 2 achieved."
